  "prompt": "What are the good diets for weight loss?",
  "response": "Here are some effective diets for weight loss:\n\n1. Mediterranean Diet\n- Focuses on whole foods\n- High in fruits, vegetables, lean proteins\n- Heart-healthy and sustainable\n\n2. Low-Carb Diet\n- Reduces carbohydrate intake\n- Increases protein and healthy fats\n- Examples: Keto, Atkins\n\n3. Intermittent Fasting\n- Alternating periods of eating and fasting\n- Can help reduce calorie intake\n- Multiple approaches (16/8, 5:2)\n\n4. DASH Diet\n- Designed to lower blood pressure\n- Emphasizes fruits, vegetables, whole grains\n- Low in sodium\n\n5. Plant-Based Diet\n- Focuses on fruits, vegetables, legumes\n- Low in processed foods\n- Can support weight loss and overall health\n\n6. Weight Watchers (WW)\n- Points-based system\n- Flexible eating plan\n- Provides community support\n\n7. Paleo Diet\n- Based on foods presumed eaten by early humans\n- Whole foods, lean proteins\n- Eliminates processed foods\n\nKey principles for all diets:\n- Calorie deficit\n- Balanced nutrition\n- Regular exercise\n- Sustainable lifestyle changes\n\nAlways consult a healthcare professional before starting any new diet.",
